{{Documentation subpage}}
<!----Categories where indicated at the bottom of the page, please; interwikis to Wikidata.---->

== Usage ==
 <nowiki>{{tim|ifdef}}</nowiki>
{{tim|ifdef}} offers links to a template (only) available on Meta.

== Caveats ==
At the moment it's not exactly the opposite of {{tim|tiw}} on Meta.

== See also ==
* {{lts}}
* {{Ltsmeta|tim}}
* {{Ltsmeta|tiw}}
* {{Lts|ltsmeta}}
* {{Lts|tiw}} is at the moment different from [[m:Template:Tiw|Meta]].

